<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<title>wǒ shǔ zhǔ 迦南436</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 wǒ shǔ zhǔ, wǒ shǔ zhǔ, wǒ yǒng yuǎn dōu shǔ yú zhǔ,
 zǒu dào nǎ lǐ huó dào hé nián, zhǔ de cí ài cóng bù gǎi biàn,
 wǒ suī bù hǎo, zhǔ réng ài wǒ wǒ de míng zì zhǔ jì zài xīn zhōng.
 zǒu dào nǎ lǐ huó dào hé nián, wǒ de xīn nǎ bù néng gǎi biàn.</lyrics>
</song>